{"tid":1126097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警長張家輝涉盜竊：案發時冇意識","createTime":"2019-04-26T06:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T08:23:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4523af25e562185a78c797fc046d27e21deea5ad","tid":1126097,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190426/20664351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F20664351&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjlHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=b51a1097\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F20664351&h=a9bb958d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190426/20664351</a><br />\n<br />\n警長張家輝涉盜竊：案發時冇意識<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190426/large/a0902a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190426%2Flarge%2Fa0902a.gif&h=3114eecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告張家輝早前捲入公職人員行為失當案被捕停職，去年受審後脫罪。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】捲入公職人員行為失當案的警長，被捕停職候審期間稱受情緒困擾，懷疑於深水埗一個特賣場偷去總值32元貨物，放入環保袋及褲袋中，由兼任輔警的店員當場捕獲。停職警長被控高買案昨日續審，他出庭自辯表示案發時「冇意識」，否認有心將貨品放入袋中；其妻供稱被告在行為失當案感覺被誣衊，行為變得幼稚兼常發脾氣，在八號風球下堅持跑步。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱感自責及常哭泣<br />\n<br />\n被告張家輝（51歲）自辯稱2015年10月被廉署拘捕，停職至今，他會「周圍行」及做運動打發時間。他指因該案受情緒困擾及面對很大壓力，至三年多後、即去年5月發生今次盜竊案，他開始自責及經常哭泣，一周後看精神科醫生。去年10月，他受審後脫罪。<br />\n<br />\n店舖閉路電視拍到疑是部份貨物被盜過程，顯示被告從貨架拿起一支LED燈細看及嘗試開燈，然後用提着環保袋的手拿着燈並垂低手，貨品數秒後消失，但關鍵一刻被其他顧客下半身遮蔽，後來貨品在被告的環保袋尋回。<br />\n<br />\n被告供稱當時毋須購買涉案物品，被問為何要拿起貨品時，他稱「我都唔知點解，（當時）腦海一片空白，我都唔知點樣解釋」，惟否認有心不付款。<br />\n<br />\n被告妻供稱，丈夫受廉署案困擾期間暴瘦20磅，經常心不在焉及哭泣，對別人說話沒反應，嚴重時怕人怕得乘車也要別人陪伴，她游說超過一年丈夫才同意求診。案件今午裁決。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3886/18<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n趁Supper Moment表演 青年涉非禮兩女fans<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n冒迪士尼前員工賣套票 女文員囚11個月"},{"pid":"5ad337d325467de379c5dc34eef381c59ba6ee93","tid":1126097,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"脫罪？"},{"pid":"9b82fea19eeaa13fbcf1868f42b33d915698d4f2","tid":1126097,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"真.渣渣輝"},{"pid":"ea903e93bb526c270d955102323ad8c8b73eaf60","tid":1126097,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"無咗靈魂"},{"pid":"f05aff919ee93fdf3e47037ed12156409e5f831a","tid":1126097,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Le3ZO6rugmtptUDLa3B2Kg--~B/aD00MDA7dz02MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant_TW/News/YahooOmg/20140408182025_tw_omg_news_564567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLe3ZO6rugmtptUDLa3B2Kg--~B%2FaD00MDA7dz02MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant_TW%2FNews%2FYahooOmg%2F20140408182025_tw_omg_news_564567.jpg&h=8b997ad2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62de5c715524b3195a0ad6d356914a041c43dd4c","tid":1126097,"uid":41204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEySpFx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEySpFx.jpg&h=d73db6a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5427db8c656c7a932d6ecab37ee0d6aca8e8d940","tid":1126097,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"冇意識犯事唔係更加危險？應該送入青山啦下話？"},{"pid":"31af88c0521772f623c764b8fac0aff3fdb7effe","tid":1126097,"uid":201768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"好地地拍戲咪幾好"},{"pid":"96f65c43067d3ccba3945ee651fbfa5441ddc886","tid":1126097,"uid":88862,"like":0,"di